{"tid":1241814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【全港運動會】623禮賓府擲蛋活動日","createTime":"2019-06-19T00:08:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T00:58:12.000Z","uid":51814,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"763078fdcb15dea9b37d51acd2c304c276d21df5","tid":1241814,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:08:54.000Z","msg":"各位香港市民你好，我係淋病，大家對我昨天的記招滿意嗎？<br />\n<br />\n為了推廣一帶一路，我出任增城道教協進會主席，所以常常把增城的道協掛在咀邊，讓各位香港人明白道教是多麼好，除了上帝以外還有這個選擇。<br />\n<br />\n我也聽取了六大宗教領袖們的見議，同意落實在逃犯條例中對宗教人仕獲得零豁免。我亦將會在警隊中加入哈利路亞速龍小隊，在清場時唱詩歌為香港人打氣。<br />\n<br />\n我會繼續服務香港市民，聆聽大家的心聲，只是到現在為止，都沒有看到一位市民表達意見，你們能幫我嗎？<br />\n<br />\n今個星期日，將你對特區政府嘅訴求，寫在雞蛋上面，直接擲入來禮賓府給我看看，我希望上次出來遊行的38萬人，每人也給我最少1打雞蛋。放心！今次警隊也可以參與這個活動，包括支援的公安們。<br />\n<br />\n6月23日，我就在禮賓府等候，不撤不散！"},{"pid":"4d06902e7e9ea5de0f03ea82a5409be63a0e2cd3","tid":1241814,"uid":262690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:10:00.000Z","msg":"雞蛋革命"},{"pid":"444baece3215d1a5c3f9aa1631d817eb2b1ae0e9","tid":1241814,"uid":231523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:10:27.000Z","msg":"621"},{"pid":"c928154984abd4b7c4171f66680f50834b0855b3","tid":1241814,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:15:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc1f6cdb06134450589e0921c39e617c8e5dfda5","tid":1241814,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d06902e7e9ea5de0f03ea82a5409be63a0e2cd3","tid":1241814,"uid":262690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:10:00.000Z","msg":"雞蛋革命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:29:39.000Z","msg":"除了雞蛋，也可以用鴨蛋，鳥蛋，扭蛋"},{"pid":"5085c4a315bcd334e48e4663c5347ead5efeb11b","tid":1241814,"uid":169207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:30:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">*******請廣傳*******<br />\n地點：立法會<br />\n620晚上 詩歌禱告馬拉松<br />\n621全日 美食節<br />\n<br />\n#雞蛋是必吃的<br />\n#番茄也好好味<br />\n*******請廣傳*******</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8958c633f2f14a96127bb7c620c5ae68c58b3153","tid":1241814,"uid":122676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:31:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54ec4ad3e7ef9ea126057d86e3dc5acdaa8061eb","tid":1241814,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597e643a223c27ca737705663c211f1c265188f5","tid":1241814,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:58:12.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}